lenders.name: Jake Ferguson
lenders.occupational_info:
If you've found yourself dealing with a financial hardship, not knowing how or where you will get the money to pay your debts, Long Beach Auto Title Loans may be able to help! Our only requirement is that you own your vehicle free and clear. This is all it takes to be eligible. Credit is not a major factor. We will give you a sum of money based on the equity in your vehicle. All you have to do is let us hold onto your title while you continue driving your vehicle as normal. It's really quite easy.

When you apply, you'll need to bring these items: Your clear title, proof or insurance, current driver's license, proof of income (2 most recent pay stubs) and proof of residence (current utility bill). We should have an answer for you in as little as 24 hours! Don't wait! Fill out the form on our website to start the process. If you have any questions, give our title loan professionals a call at (562) 392-8693 today!
